@startuml
title D1: Search for Patient Information

actor "User (Doctor/Staff)" as User
participant "Frontend (UI)\n(PatientSearch.tsx)" as UI
participant "PatientController\n(app/routers/patients.py)" as API
participant "CRUD Layer\n(crud.py)" as CRUD
database "PostgreSQL\nDatabase" as DB

User -> UI: Enter search criteria\n(Name, ID, or Phone)
activate UI

UI -> API: GET /patients/search?query={criteria}
activate API

API -> CRUD: get_patients_by_filter(criteria)
activate CRUD

CRUD -> DB: SELECT * FROM patients\nWHERE name ILIKE criteria...
activate DB

DB --> CRUD: Return matching records
deactivate DB

CRUD --> API: Return List[Patient]
deactivate CRUD

API --> UI: Return JSON response
deactivate API

UI -> UI: Render patient list
UI --> User: Display search results
deactivate UI

@enduml